    <h1>Etsy Privacy Policy Generator</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Published July 22, 2026</p>

    <p>Etsy does not provide a built-in privacy policy generator for sellers. The platform requires every shop owner to handle their own privacy disclosures, but it does not offer a tool to create one. To get a privacy policy that reflects your specific Etsy shop's data practices, you need an external generator that asks about the services you use, the data you collect through orders, and which privacy laws apply to your buyers. A <a href="https://buildprivacypolicy.com/">free privacy policy generator</a> walks you through targeted questions about your Etsy shop's setup and produces a ready-to-use policy you can paste into your shop's policies section or host for free, with no signup or payment required.</p>

    <p>This guide covers everything Etsy sellers need to know: whether Etsy requires a privacy policy, why your shop needs one even if it is not legally mandated in your jurisdiction, what your policy should include to cover buyer data and third-party services, how to add it to your Etsy shop step by step, and how to generate one in minutes.</p>

    <nav class="toc">
      <p class="toc-title">Contents</p>
